getTemplates

public List<DependencyTreeTransformer> getTemplates(int rangeType)
Returns all possible templates for this property. Properties whose range is a boolean or a PolicyGrid utility Date have a different template set.

Parameters:
rangeType - Datatype of property: 2 for dates, 5 for boolean, other types do not matter.
